/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:1:# DA-panta-root: Panta is the per-project virtual root above all rheis
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:25:Introduce **Panta**: a single, per-project, *virtual* root node that sits above
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:26:all rheis and their tickets. It is the default place rheis are added and the
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:27:single anchor for a project-wide unified view. The name follows *panta rhei* —
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:28:the still root that contains all the flows. §FS-rhei-panta
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:30:## 1. Position in the hierarchy
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:32:The node hierarchy gains one level at the top:
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:35:Panta            level 0   kind `panta`   (virtual, one per project)
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:37:    └── Task     level 2+  kind `task`…   (a ticket — a unit of work)
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:41:node: a rhei is now *a node among siblings* under Panta rather than the top of
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:42:its own isolated tree. `panta` becomes the new reserved, virtual root kind and
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:50:Panta reuses the Directory Workspace merge mechanism rather than inventing a new
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:52:(§FS-rhei-plan-language.1.2); under Panta, the rheis in a project merge into one
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:56:- Status rolls up Panta ← rheis ← tickets through one uniform tree walk.
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:57:- A project loads as one graph rooted at Panta instead of N disconnected plans.
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:64:Creating a rhei without naming a parent attaches it under Panta. Panta is the
