/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:67:allowed directly under Panta, giving an inbox for unfiled work.
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:71:Panta has no authored heading and no node file of its own, so there is nothing
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:85:- **A real, authored Panta heading.** Author Panta as an explicit top-of-file
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:95:- **ID namespacing.** A ticket's project-wide identity is its rhei id joined with
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:96:  its rhei-local task id (a dotted Panta path). This yields cross-rhei
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:98:  rules and grammar productions are deferred to §AR-rhei-panta.
/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/docs/decisions/architectural/panta-root.md:100:  the `rhei` root to the `panta` root; rheis gain their own node profile. The
